  <item rdf:about="2024/0609-kamakura/">
            <title>2024/06/09: 鎌倉ハイキング</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2024/0609-kamakura/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>紫陽花シーズン。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9753.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9753.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9753.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9753.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9753"/></a></p>

<p>定点観測。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9755.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9755.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9755.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9755.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9755"/></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2024-2024-06T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

